title: Amazing Wallpapers - Mega Pack - 2011 Edition
description:
=============================================
Amazing Wallpapers - Mega Pack - 2011 Edition
=============================================

A pack of (relatively) high-res images suitable for use as backgrounds.
Unmodified except where rotation was necessary.

Format: JPEG
Resolution: Multiple size
Number of wallpaper: 1,000+
Quality: HD (with some in Normal quality)

Wallpaper Categories:
Abstract, Animal, Artistic, Cartoon, Celebrity
Comics, Game, Holiday, Military, Misc, Movie, Music
Photography, Products, Sci Fi
TV Show, Technology
Vehicles, Video Game, Women
...etc

They are available in most popular screen resolutions, so you can pick-and-choose the folder(s) for your computer(s).

You can freely distribute these photos! I'd be thrilled to hear your feedback!
